жWilliam George King
17th May 2002 - 9th November 2020
'A heart is not judged by how much you love;
but by how much you are loved by others'
Always in our thoughts"н
кCAMPBELL CRICHTON MACKINNON BURNAP
10 September 1939 - 30 May 2008
